                    <h2>Form layout</h2>
                    <p>By default, all input fields have width set to 100%. Its size is dependent to its parent element. This makes it possible set up the form layout at a higher level, and also in each <a href="#forms">formelement</a> by using <a href="/#grid">the grid system</a>.</p>
